      "description": "The CFD hemolysis prediction model shall be validated using experimental data obtained from physical bench-top or in-vitro testing of the centrifugal blood pump under representative CPB operating conditions. Experimental validation is required to confirm that simulated shear-stress distributions and resulting hemolysis indices correspond to measured outcomes.",
      "requiredVerificationMethod": "experimental-validation",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Relative hemolysis index (RH) predicted by CFD shall agree with experimentally measured values to within 20% across all five target flow-speed operating points."
    }
