    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The literature review of published hemolysis data demonstrated that CFD predictions of relative hemolysis index are consistent with reported values across the full CPB operating envelope. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per the assessment plan. The model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
